<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Student Details</title>

```
<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #e6f2ff; /* light blue */
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
        text-align: center;
        color: #004080;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        background: white;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    p {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin: 10px 0;
        color: #333;
    }

    strong {
        color: #004080;
    }

    a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #0066cc;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-right: 10px;
    }

    a:hover {
        color: #003366;
    }

    .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .edit-btn {
        background-color: #66b3ff;
        color: white;
    }

    .edit-btn:hover {
        background-color: #3399ff;
    }

    .delete-btn {
        background-color: #ff6666;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .delete-btn:hover {
        background-color: #cc0000;
    }

    .back-link {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }
</style>
```

</head>

<body>
    <h1>Student Details</h1>

```
<div class="container">
    <p><strong>ID:</strong> <%= student._id %></p>
    <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= student.name %></p>
    <p><strong>Age:</strong> <%= student.age %></p>
    <p><strong>Course:</strong> <%= student.course %></p>

    <a href="/student/<%= student._id %>/edit" class="btn edit-btn">Edit</a>

    <form action="/student/<%= student._id %>?_method=DELETE" method="POST" style="display:inline;">
        <button type="submit" class="btn delete-btn">Delete</button>
    </form>

    <a href="/students" class="back-link">← Back to List</a>
</div>
```

</body>

</html>
